title: Lenka Hiklová
text: Lenka Hiklová, née Lackovičová (born March 8, 1980), of the "HK Kamenná Chata" is a <a href="Slovakia">Slovakian</a> <a href="ski%20mountaineer">ski mountaineer</a>. Amongst others, she finished eighth in the team event of the <a href="2003%20European%20Championship%20of%20Ski%20Mountaineering">2003 European Championship of Ski Mountaineering</a>, together with <a href="Anna%20Pa%C5%BEitn%C3%A1">Anna Pažitná</a>.
